sorrow  忧伤

collide 碰撞


sorrow collide
悲伤碰撞


composed = calmed  released  harmed
平静释放伤害

charmed by a day
一整天都怅惘

sublime silence
高高在上的沉默

foreign land await for your sign
等待你涉足的外乡地界

Now I'm a nomad as I wade through silence
现在我只是一个涉水的游牧之人

Far away and not quite in time
很远，也不太及时

disgracing our minds
让我们的思想蒙羞

disgrace  使蒙羞；给…带来耻辱；


adrift    漂泊

